Firewall Configuration (UFW)

1. Installed UFW
sudo apt update
sudo apt install ufw -y

2. Allowed required ports

Allow SSH:
sudo ufw allow ssh

Allow HTTP:
sudo ufw allow 80

Allow application port:
sudo ufw allow 8000

3. Restricted SSH access to specific IP

sudo ufw allow from <YOUR-IP> to any port 22
sudo ufw delete allow ssh

4. Enabled firewall

sudo ufw enable

5. Verified firewall status

sudo ufw status

Output:
Status: active

To                         Action      From
--                         ------      ----
22/tcp                     ALLOW       <YOUR-IP>
80/tcp                     ALLOW       Anywhere
8000/tcp                   ALLOW       Anywhere
